videos.headline: Jackson gives Louisville the lead with 71-yard TD pass
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson launches a deep pass to James Quick for a 71-yard touchdown, giving the Cardinals the early lead over Marshall.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jackson gives Louisville the lead with 71-yard TD pass) 2016/09/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson's dominance transfers over against Marshall
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson continues to put on a show week after week, this time going for four passing touchdowns and one rushing score in the first half against Marshall.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lamar Jackson's dominance transfers over against Marshall) 2016/09/24 ESHEET ENHL
